The following examples display how the {{Path|gentoo.conf}} file can be set up in the {{Path|/etc/portage/repos.conf/}} directory. For more information visit the [[Project:Portage/Sync#Portage_configuration|Portage Sync article]].

{{FileBox|filename=gentoo.conf|title=Git gentoo.conf configuration using the GitHub mirror|lang=ini|1=
[DEFAULT]
main-repo = gentoo

[gentoo]
location = /usr/portage
sync-type = git
sync-uri = https://github.com/gentoo/gentoo-portage-rsync-mirror
auto-sync = yes
}}
